channel.description: Hi when i run my server after about 5mins it comes up with unbale to run port all ready in use when its the only server ive got up i have windows visa and have done the firewall thing but still it comes up can some 1 help me

item.dc:creator: @ChemicalReaction1 ChemicalReaction™
item.description:
@ChemicalReaction1 wrote:

Ok then. go into your server.java
Search 43594
Change that to 5555 or something like that…
And now thats your port, And any other thing running previously is running on 43594. so you should be able to connect.
